00:00:06.254 --> 00:00:09.974
We looked at how to evaluate our market size, our market trends,

00:00:09.974 --> 00:00:11.699
run a competitor analysis,

00:00:11.699 --> 00:00:15.359
and we even looked at how we measure and compare our marketing channels.

00:00:15.359 --> 00:00:18.859
We also saw the importance of measuring our net promoter score.

00:00:18.859 --> 00:00:23.044
Now I know it feels like a lot but we've really only scratched the surface.

00:00:23.045 --> 00:00:25.580
As you continue in your marketing endeavor,

00:00:25.579 --> 00:00:29.000
you'll find new and exciting ways to measure and model data.

00:00:29.000 --> 00:00:31.399
