00:00:31.399 --> 00:00:34.429
skills and the knowledge on how to apply them.

00:00:34.429 --> 00:00:37.399
From here, you'll be familiar enough to approach

00:00:37.399 --> 00:00:40.820
most marketing questions in analytics projects that will come your way,

00:00:40.820 --> 00:00:43.340
and you're ready to start investigating the data on

00:00:43.340 --> 00:00:47.190
your next project to find where you can take action.

